# =============================================================================
# Security and Authentication
# =============================================================================

# For production deployments, consider:
# 1. Using Kubernetes secrets for sensitive values
# 2. Enabling TLS for all connections
# 3. Implementing proper NATS authentication (NKeys, JWT)
# 4. Network policies and security groups
# 5. Regular security updates and patches

# Example secret management (not in this file - use Kubernetes secrets):
# kubectl create secret generic nats-auth \
#   --from-literal=synadia-nkey="YOUR_NKEY" \
